<H3> <TI>   PLO Asks Helsinki To Upgrade Mission to Embassy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PLO Asks Helsinki To Upgrade Mission to Embassy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0405165294 Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network in Finnish 
1430 GMT 4 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0405165294 </F>
<F P=104>  Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Finnish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Palestine Liberation Organization, PLO, would 
like to raise the diplomatic status of its information offices 
in the Nordic countries. The PLO representative in Finland is 
appealing to the Finnish Government to raise the matter at a 
Nordic foreign ministers's meeting which starts in Reykjavik 
tomorrow. The PLO says that if Finland, as the first Nordic 
country, were to set an example in this matter, the Palestinians 
would value this as much as they value the contributions of 
Norway and Sweden in the Middle East peace process. 

</TEXT>

