<F P=100> CYPRUS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Turkey Reportedly Prepares Plan To Occupy Cyprus </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Turkey Reportedly Prepares Plan To Occupy Cyprus </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0305121294 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network in Greek 1030 GMT 3 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0305121294 </F>
<F P=104>  Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network </F>

<F P=105>  Greek </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Turkey has prepared a plan to occupy all of Cyprus 
and has asked Islamic countries for support. Two of them have 
already replied positively. 
  The Arab newspaper AL MUHARRIR, which is published in Paris, 
has revealed this information crediting well-informed Turkish 
diplomatic sources. The newspaper adds that, according to the 
Turkish sources, Cyprus has been selected as a center for 
laundering dirty money made from drug trafficking, secret arms 
selling, and violations of the embargo against Yugoslavia. They 
also claim that there is cooperation between Russia, Yugoslavia, 
and Cypriot Orthodox people to suppress the Muslims. 

</TEXT>

