<H3> <TI>   Muslim Group Members Detained for Illegal Activities </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Muslim Group Members Detained for Illegal Activities </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0405135794 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 
GMT 4 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0405135794 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Twenty-one members of an organization named Muslim 
Youth [Musluman Genclik], which aims at establishing an order 
based on religious principles in Turkey, were captured in 
Istanbul for engaging in illegal activities. The suspects are 
reported to belong to the radical religious sector. Many 
weapons and bombs were found in the suspects' possession. 

