<F P=102>   TA0405184094 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
GMT 4 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0405184094 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
