<F P=100> FRANCE </F>
<H3> <TI>   Mitterand Sends Message To Nelson Mandela </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Mitterand Sends Message To Nelson Mandela </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0405215694 Paris Radio France International in French 2130 
GMT 4 May 94 </F>

