<H3> <TI>   Scepticism Over Eurofighter Remains `Undiminished' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Scepticism Over Eurofighter Remains `Undiminished' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0505110294 London FINANCIAL TIMES in English 5 May 94 p 
2--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM0505110294 </F>
<F P=104>  London FINANCIAL TIMES </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


