<H4>    Denies Claim of Obstructing Media </H4>

<F P=102> NC0505145594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in 
Greek 1130 GMT 5 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0505145594 </F>
<F P=104>  Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network </F>
