<H3> <TI>   Vienna Croat-Muslim Talks End; To Resume </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Vienna Croat-Muslim Talks End; To Resume </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0705205994 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 
2000 GMT 7 May 94 </F>

