<H3> <TI>   Iranian Embassy Denies Links With Terrorists </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Iranian Embassy Denies Links With Terrorists </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0605175794 Athens ATHENS NEWS in English 6 May 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> NC0605175794 </F>
<F P=104>  Athens ATHENS NEWS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Iranian embassy in Athens yesterday strongly 
denied a report in Britain's INDEPENDENT newspaper that Tehran 
had offered guns to the urban guerrilla groups November 17, of 
Greece, and the IRA, of Northern Ireland, in exchange for the 
assassination of Iranian dissidents in Europe. It also rejected 
allegations it had used drug trafficking money to sponsor 
international terrorist activities. 

