<H3> <TI>   Bomb Explodes at Prosperity Party Istanbul Office </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bomb Explodes at Prosperity Party Istanbul Office </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0705105594 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 0910 GMT 7 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA0705105594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Istanbul, May 7 (A.A) -- Two people were wounded 
when unidentified people threw a bomb at the office of the 
fundamentalist Prosperity Party (RP) in Bayrampasa District of 
the town. 
  AA reporter was told by security officials that the attacks 
took place around 21.00 hours local time when two people threw 
the bomb at the office and escaped. 
  Windows of near-by buildings were shattered and the office 
suffered great material damage, it was reported. 
  It was later determined that the bomb was a Russian made 
"fragment effect" bomb. 
  The wounded were immediately taken to hospital, police said 
adding a wide-scale operation was started in the area to catch 
the assailants. 

</TEXT>

