<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over still of Defense Minister Golhan] </F>
  [Text] National Defense Minister Mehmet Golhan has said 
that the delivery of 20 Super Puma helicopters Turkey bought 
from the French-German Eurocopter company will begin in 1995. 
  Golhan, who is on an official visit to France, toured 
